snippet: The Democratic candidates vying for Christine C. Quinn’s seat in Chelsea hold similar positions on many issues, but that hasn’t stopped the mudslinging.
abstract: Trailside blog; campaigns of Democratic candidates vying for Christine C Quinn's City Council seat in Chelsea have turned vicious, despite fact that candidates hold similar positions on many issues.
lead_paragraph: The Democratic candidates vying for Christine C. Quinn’s seat in Chelsea hold similar positions on many issues, but that hasn’t stopped the mudslinging.
